Package com.github.dscpsyl.jgrade2

Class Grader

java.lang.Object
com.github.dscpsyl.jgrade2.Grader
public class Grader extends Object
A class to encompass all of the options for grading tests. Bundles together GradedTestResults, a total score, a total max score, any output relevant to the entire submission, and a timer feature for timing execution time. Is Observable to OutputFormatters.

      public void setGraderStrategy(GraderStrategy s)

    • runJUnitGradedTests

      public void runJUnitGradedTests(Class<?> testSuite)
      Runs JUnit tests and attaches a GradedTestListener to listen for all GradedTests and add the created GradedTestResults. If class MyTests has graded test JUnit test methods, then call this method with MyTests.class. Can alter the list of results added from the run by setting the GraderStrategy.
      Parameters:
      testSuite - The class containing the tests.
